This directory includes dataset statistics extracting scripts. The results are saved on the directories below:
    Processed-Kitap
    Processed-MC4
    Processed-Oscar
    Processed-SketchEngine

Under these directories, there are 3 kinds of files:
    1- The summary files that has the resulting statistics.
    2- The xxxx_data_formatted files that include the data formatted as JSON lines.
    3- The xxxx_stats_formatted files that include the data statistics for each samples.

The summary files are contained in the repository, but the xxxx_data_formatted and xxxx_stats_formatted 
can be found under the "/userfiles/merdogan18/data_statistics" directory in the KUACC cluster.
    